# Casino Games API

The **Casino Games API** provides access to a list of games offered by the casino platform.  
It allows developers to fetch game details such as name, provider, category, features (jackpot, free spins, multipliers),  
and configuration settings like RTP, volatility, and availability status.  

---

## Example Endpoint

```http
GET /api/v1/games

SAMPLE RESPONSE



[
  {
    "gameId": "slot123",
    "name": "Mega Fortune Deluxe",
    "provider": "NetEnt",
    "category": "slots",
    "features": {
      "jackpot": true,
      "freeSpins": true,
      "multiplier": false
    },
    "launchUrl": "https://casino-api.example.com/games/slot123/play",
    "thumbnail": "https://cdn.casino.com/images/games/slot123.png",
    "status": "active",
    "rtp": 96.5,
    "volatility": "high",
    "demoAvailable": true
  },
  {
    "gameId": "bj101",
    "name": "Blackjack Classic",
    "provider": "Playtech",
    "category": "blackjack",
    "features": {
      "jackpot": false,
      "freeSpins": false,
      "multiplier": false
    },
    "launchUrl": "https://casino-api.example.com/games/bj101/play",
    "thumbnail": "https://cdn.casino.com/images/games/bj101.png",
    "status": "active",
    "rtp": 99.5,
    "volatility": "low",
    "demoAvailable": false
  }
]


## üìñ Attribute Reference

| Attribute            | Type          | Mandatory | Description                                    | If TRUE / Value Present                | If FALSE / Missing                      |
|-----------------------|---------------|-----------|------------------------------------------------|----------------------------------------|-----------------------------------------|
| `gameId`             | String        | ‚úÖ Yes    | Unique identifier of the game.                 | Required, identifies the game.         | Cannot be missing.                      |
| `name`               | String        | ‚úÖ Yes    | Display name of the game.                      | Game shows with this name.             | Game may not display properly.          |
| `provider`           | String        | ‚úÖ Yes    | Vendor or studio providing the game.           | Used for filtering by provider.        | Defaults to "Unknown".                  |
| `category`           | String        | ‚úÖ Yes    | Type of game (slots, roulette, blackjack).     | Helps in filtering/search.             | Game may not appear in filtered lists.  |
| `features.jackpot`   | Boolean       | ‚ùå No     | Progressive jackpot availability.              | Jackpot banner/prize pool shown.       | No jackpot displayed.                   |
| `features.freeSpins` | Boolean       | ‚ùå No     | Free spin bonus availability.                  | Free spins available in gameplay.      | No free spins possible.                 |
| `features.multiplier`| Boolean       | ‚ùå No     | Multiplier mechanic availability.              | Multipliers applied in gameplay.       | No multipliers offered.                 |
| `launchUrl`          | String (URL)  | ‚úÖ Yes    | Secure link to launch the game.                | Game can be launched.                  | Game cannot be started.                 |
| `thumbnail`          | String (URL)  | ‚ùå No     | Game image thumbnail.                          | Shown in casino lobby.                 | Default/blank image shown.              |
| `status`             | String (enum) | ‚úÖ Yes    | Game status (`active`, `inactive`, `maintenance`). | `active` ‚Üí playable.                   | Hidden/disabled if not active.          |
| `rtp`                | Number (float)| ‚ùå No     | Return to Player % (e.g., 96.5).               | RTP displayed in info/help.            | Hidden or default RTP applies.          |
| `volatility`         | String (enum) | ‚ùå No     | Payout variance (`low`, `medium`, `high`).     | Shown in game details.                 | Not displayed.                          |
| `demoAvailable`      | Boolean       | ‚ùå No     | Whether demo/free play is available.           | Players can try for free.              | Only real money mode.                   |
